import {Reactstrap} from ''


function Footer(params) {

    return(
        <Card
        className="my-2"
        style={{
          width: '18rem'
        }}
      >
        <CardHeader>
          Header
        </CardHeader>
        <CardBody>
          <CardTitle tag="h5">
            Special Title Treatment
          </CardTitle>
          <CardText>
            With supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
          </CardText>
          <Button>
            Go somewhere
          </Button>
        </CardBody>
        <CardFooter>
          Footer
        </CardFooter>
      </Card>
        
        


        
    )
    
}
export default Footer
